Package: sparsevar
Version: 0.0.11
Date: 2019-08-19
Title: Sparse VAR/VECM Models Estimation
Authors@R: c(person("Simone", "Vazzoler", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "svazzole@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Simone Vazzoler <svazzole@gmail.com>
